===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|ذُو القَعْدَةِ}}''' {{IPAchar|(ðu l-qáʕda)}} {{m}}

#[[Dhu al-Qi'dah]], the eleventh of the twelve months of the Muslim lunar calendar, each beginning with a [[new moon]]. [[Dhu al-Qi'dah]] means "master of the truce" in Arabic, and pagan Arabs did not conduct war during this month.

